      "content": "but talking doesn't change the facts. the universe doesn't care about my feelings and there is no higher purpose or cosmic meaning waiting to be found. it's just physics and entropy. even the people trying to \"help\" are just distracting me from the truth that everything eventually just fades into nothing.",
